ese individuals to leverage Kubernetes effectively, improve application performance, enhance security, and reduce operational costs. Furthermore, organizations that invest in training their workforce in Kubernetes will gain a competitive advantage by accelerating their adoption of cloud-native technologies and improving their ability to innovate."
